org.vanilladb.core.storage.metadata.statistics

Class Histogram

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vanilladb.core.storage.metadata.statistics.Histogram

  • public class Histogram
extends Object
    A histogram that, for each field of a table, approximates the distribution of values using buckets.

    Assumes that, for each field:

    • Sets of records in different buckets are disjoint.
    • Sets of values in different buckets are disjoint.
